commentable_entity.ask: Have David Brown fired for slander of Johnny Depp
commentable_entity.title: The Times UK: Have David Brown fired for slander of Johnny Depp
commentable_entity.description: David Brown has been helping spread lies about Johnny Depp and defending Amber Heard, who was abusing Johnny Depp. David Brown is probably trying to use this as a way to get his name out there, however, like the judge in the case, he has ignored all of Depp’s evidence and thrown out what little journalistic integrity he has. He deserves to be fired for this slander. We should not allow someone who has ignored evidence and testimony be allowed to gain anything by dragging the name of a great a man as Johnny Depp.
commentable_entity.letter_body: Have David Brown fired for slander of Johnny Depp
